snippet.title: Into Samomor (Gameplay Trailer #1)
snippet.description:
#gamedev #indiegame #indiegames 
An RPG for those who like to decide people's fates and explore their deepest secrets. Solve the mystery case of 19 missing people in Samomor town and figure out who the liar is.

🔥 Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2373890/Into_Samomor/

Twitter (X): https://twitter.com/intosamomor
